(16, 'Featured Expert - How to Write a Business Plan with Melinda Emerson, SmallBiz Lady ', 9, 42, 2, '', 'Featured Expert - How to Write a Business Plan with Melinda Emerson, SmallBiz Lady ', 'http://www.kaltura.com/index.php/kwidget/cache_st/1333032904/wid/_737192/uiconf_id/7642702/entry_id/1_t5py5sds', 'http://www.kaltura.com/index.php/kwidget/cache_st/1333032904/wid/_737192/uiconf_id/7642702/entry_id/1_t5py5sds', 6, '<p>Every small business needs a plan for success. Simply stated, a business plan is your strategy for bringing your product or service to the marketplace. <br />\r\n  In this chapter, Melinda Emerson, SmallBiz Lady, will help you pull together your road map for reaching your business destination.Â  Her articles, included in this chapter, will walk you step by step through writing a business plan. </p>\r\n<p>Be sure to listen to her podcast in which Melinda discusses the five things that people are never told about starting a new business.</p>\r\n<p>Next steps to complete this chapter:</p>\r\n<p>Review your current business plan for completeness according to Melindaâ€™s process.</p>\r\n', '2012-03-05', '2012-05-24 10:05:18', '', ''),
(19, 'How Small Companies Generate Sales Using Facebook, LinkedIn, & Twitter', 9, 0, 4, '', ' (May 18, 2010 webinar) ', 'https://amfam.webex.com/ec0605l/eventcenter/recording/recordAction.do?theAction=poprecord&actname=%2Feventcenter%2Fframe%2Fg.do&apiname=lsr.php&renewticket=0&renewticket=0&actappname=ec0605l&entappname=url0107l&needFilter=false&&isurlact=true&entactname=%2FnbrRecordingURL.do&rID=39359942&rKey=2b19b9328fdda1ea&recordID=39359942&rnd=9204773840&siteurl=amfam&SP=EC&AT=pb&format=short\r\n', '', 4, '<p>Social media usage is growingâ€”not just among the young but  among your customers, too.Â  In todayâ€™s  marketing environment, you want to be found in the socially-connected world.Â  In this chapter, learn why the use of social  networks can really boost your businessâ€™s sales and how social networks work to  provide you access to the customers you want to meet most. Social media  marketing should now be part of your lead generation strategy.</p>\r\n<p>Led by the Business Acceleratorâ€™s social media coach, Dean  DeLisle, youâ€™ll learn how to properly set up your LinkedIn and Facebook  profiles for maximum search engine optimization.Â  Dean will also discuss the importance of capturing  your network on LinkedIn and making a conscious effort to connect with people  in a meaningful way everyday.Â  Heâ€™ll  discuss how to leverage LinkedIn groups to provide you access to key people you  want to connect with and call on, and how you can repurpose your slides and  other content to boost your companyâ€™s page rankings in search engine searches. </p>\r\n<p>This chapter also features Dean DeLisleâ€™s ebook, <em>9 Things You Must Know Before You Log On</em>,  and some tips by Rieva Lesonsky on how to set your social media goals and  objectives properly so you avoid burn-out.</p>\r\n<p>Next steps to complete this chapter:</p>\r\n<p>Redo your LinkedIn profile according to the suggestions  offered in this chapter.Â  Download the  LinkedIn Profile Guide Sheet.</p>\