(68, 'Featured Expert - Small Business Trends with Rieva Lesonsky ', 4, 43, 3, '', 'Featured Expert - Small Business Trends with Rieva Lesonsky ', 'http://www.kaltura.com/index.php/kwidget/cache_st/1333032834/wid/_737192/uiconf_id/7642702/entry_id/1_3d0m92sz', 'http://www.kaltura.com/index.php/kwidget/cache_st/1333032834/wid/_737192/uiconf_id/7642702/entry_id/1_3d0m92sz', 6, '<p>The environment in which small business operates is constantly changing.Â  Global trends such as social media usage and mobile information access are now affecting small business owners in a big wayâ€”making their world smaller and more competitive.</p>\r\n<p>Listen to this podcast with Rieva Lesonsky and our Business Accelerator Host, Euan Ford, as Rieva discusses some of the business trends that small business owners are facing today.Â  See how technology innovation such as mobile marketing is becoming a must-do for many small business owners if they wish to succeed in the very near future.</p>\r\n<p>Be sure to also read Rievaâ€™s articles on how to address the growing pains involved in running a small business in our fast-changing environment.</p>\r\n<p>Next steps to complete this chapter:</p>\r\n<p>Consider which trends you think are a must for you to follow in order to assure business growth.</p>\r\n', '2012-03-05', '2012-04-04 13:59:13', '', ''),
(69, 'Featured Expert - Stever Robbins podcast ', 9, 44, 3, '', 'Featured Expert - Stever Robbins podcast ', 'http://www.kaltura.com/index.php/kwidget/cache_st/1333033006/wid/_737192/uiconf_id/7642702/entry_id/1_jym5ixso', 'http://www.kaltura.com/index.php/kwidget/cache_st/1333033006/wid/_737192/uiconf_id/7642702/entry_id/1_jym5ixso', 6, '<p>How would life change if you committed to living only a life that you defined as &ldquo;extraordinary?&rdquo;Â  As an entrepreneur, we may pursue &ldquo;extraordinary&rdquo; in our careers, but completely forget our personal livesâ€”foregoing any balance and harmony between work and the life we lead outside of it.</p>\r\n<p>This chapter will include a podcast with Stever Robbins and our Business Accelerator Host, Euan Ford, as Stever discusses how entrepreneurs can grow their business, yet maintain work/life balance.Â  Listen in as Stever addresses the age-old myth that entrepreneurs have to devote their entire lives to the business.</p>\r\n<p>Be sure to also read Stever&rsquo;s articles included in this chapter on leading your team and your small business to new levels of success.</p>\r\n<p>Next steps to complete this chapter:</p>\r\n<p>Consider whether or not you are satisfied with your work/life balance.</p>\r\n', '2012-03-05', '2012-03-31 19:22:31', '', ''),
(70, 'How Small Business Can Make a Big Impact with Web Marketing', 9, 24, 7, '', '(2012 webinar) ', '/events/view/6', '', 2, '<p>When it comes to marketing on the Internet, there is so much to choose fromâ€”Social Media, Video, SEM, Podcasts, SEO, Blogs. Â  In this chapter, we discuss how small business owners with limited time, resources, and money can develop an internet marketing plan and implement it in an integrated, cost-effective manner.</p>\r\n<p>Dean DeLisle demonstrates how you can make a big impact in your bottom line by deploying e-marketing as one of your lead generation tactics.  Not only does he discuss the importance of search engine optimization and search engine marketing in the pursuit of &ldquo;being found,&rdquo; but he&rsquo;ll also explore how you integrate your social media marketing to generate better results. </p>\r\n', '2012-03-05', '2012-05-24 10:05:18', '', ''),
(71, 'Managing Your Financial Score Card ', 9, 0, 13, '', '(2012 webinar) ', '/events/view/11', '', 2, '<p>When complete and well prepared, financial statements contain an incredible amount of timely and revealing information about a businessâ€™ financial health: its strengths, vulnerabilities and challenges . . . whether or not itâ€™s on track . . . or if itâ€™s really making money. </p>\r\n<p>In this webinar with accounting professional and entrepreneur Lee Werner, youâ€™ll learn how to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Understand your key financial statements and quickly zero in on the most important numbers</li>\r\n  <li>Detect variances while thereâ€™s still time to take corrective action</li>\r\n  <li>Appreciate key financial analysis ratios and tools</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Get a firm grip on your companyâ€™s lifebloodâ€”cash flow</p>', '2012-03-05', '2012-03-26 14:49:28', '', ''),
