INSERT INTO `courses` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `created`, `modified`, `metakeywords`, `metadescription`) VALUES
(1, 'Building Your Marketing Plan: A Practical Approach', 'In todayâ€™s competitive marketplace, your success in attracting new clients depends on how clearly you can communicate the unique benefit that you offer over your competition.  The more familiar your customers are with your â€œidentity,â€ the more loyal theyâ€™ll be and the better chance theyâ€™ll recommend you to others.   Make your brand identity so clear that anyone can repeat your commercial to others.  In this course, weâ€™ll discuss the steps on how to create your businessâ€™s identity and then your marketing business plan.', '2012-01-31', '2012-03-29 15:14:50', 'marketing plan, brand identity, small business marketing plan, attract new customers', 'In todayâ€™s competitive marketplace, your success in attracting new clients depends on how clearly you can communicate the unique benefit that you offer over your co'),
(2, 'Growing Your Business to the Next Level', 'Growing your business can be a tricky endeavorâ€”do it too quickly and you risk over-expansion; wait too long and you could miss the market window. Our experts can help you evaluate whether the time is right for going to that next level or not. Youâ€™ll find the tools you need for developing your business plan and building a team for growth either now or in the future.', '2012-01-31', '2012-03-29 15:17:39', 'Small business growth, Barbara Weltman, hiring for growth, business plan', 'You will find the tools you need for developing your business plan and building a team for growth either now or in the future. '),
(3, 'Leading Your Business to Success', 'As a small business owner, you ARE the companyâ€™s leader. Everyone looks to you to understand where the company is today and where itâ€™s going next. Youâ€™re the one that sets the culture at your company. This course offers insights on how to handle the role of leader in a way that benefits the company, those that work for you, and you.', '2012-01-31', '2012-03-29 15:18:19', 'leadership, small business growth, small business owner, ', 'This course offers insights on how to handle the role of leader in a way that benefits the company, those that work for you, and you.'),
(4, 'Generating Sales with Social Media', 'Meeting the sales goals youâ€™ve laid out in your business growth plan means building awareness of your company and its products or services in a plethora of ways. For small businesses, one of the least expensive, yet highly effective, approaches is social media. To maximize your results, you need to understand the different aspects of social media marketing and how to go from generating leads to generating sales. This course shows you the opportunities that social media can offer your company.', '2012-01-31', '2012-03-29 15:22:23', 'sales, lead generation, sales pitch, networking, referrals', 'You canâ€™t close sales if you donâ€™t have leads, so maximizing the lead generation processes in your company is critical for business growth.'),
(6, 'Communicating Wisely: Marketing Tactics for Small Business', 'Developing a sound marketing plan means utilizing tactics that will reach your audience in a cost-effective manner. While many small business owners think they canâ€™t afford to do marketing, quite the opposite is trueâ€”they canâ€™t afford not to. This course points out the many ways to approach marketing with the small-business-pocketbook in mind, from free PR to e-newsletters.', '2012-01-31', '2012-03-29 15:15:42', 'marketing on a budget, small budget marketing, affordable marketing, marketing tips, ', 'Developing a marketing plan means utilizing tactics that will reach your audience in a cost-effective manner. This course points out the many ways to approach marketi'),
(7, 'Leveraging the Power of Digital Marketing', 'With every business seemingly on the web these days, how do you make your web presence powerful? Itâ€™s more than just having a jazzy website. You now need to have a Facebook page, a blog, perhaps a Twitter account and an e-newsletter. For your e-marketing efforts to really sing, you need to be optimized and integrated. This course can help you make sure that you can be found and that youâ€™re generating leads successfully with your e-marketing plan.', '2012-01-31', '2012-03-29 15:16:04', 'e-marketing, creating leads, emarketing tips', 'This course can help you make sure that you can be found and that you are generating leads successfully with your e-marketing plan.'),
(8, 'Marketing Planning Tips for Small Business with Scott Cooper', '<p>Through his videos and articles, marketing strategist and author Scott Cooper shares his insights on the essential ingredients of an effective marketing plan and how to put it together. This course includes topics such as:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Understanding what marketing actually is</li>\r\n  <li>Positioning and defining your message </li>\r\n  <li>Targeting</li>\r\n  <li>Setting strategies</li>\r\n  <li>Customer relationship marketing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Plan evaluation</p>\r\n', '2012-01-31', '2012-03-29 15:16:25', 'marketing tips, Scott Cooper, setting marketing strategies, CRM, marketing plan, creating a marketing plan', 'Marketing strategist and author Scott Cooper shares his insights on the essential ingredients of an effective marketing plan and how to put it together. '),
(9, 'Selling for Entrepreneurs', 'As a business owner, you are your companyâ€™s number one sales person whether you realize it or not. Learn to make sales your priorityâ€”and how to be successful at it, too. This course reveals some of the secrets that top sales people know.  Youâ€™ll also discover how to bring sales activities into your daily routine and how to use your personality, and that of your prospect, to successfully close deals. Go from being a reluctant sales person to a real â€œgo-giver.â€', '2012-01-31', '2012-03-29 15:21:36', 'sales secrets, sales tips, increase sales, selling for entrepreneurs ', 'As a business owner, you are your companyâ€™s number one sales person whether you realize it or not. Learn to make sales your priority and how to be successful at it,'),
(11, 'Mastering the Sale', 'Being a salesperson requires skill and if, as a business owner, youâ€™ve never had formal sales training, this course can facilitate your growth as the leader of your companyâ€™s sales. Discover how the buying process actually works and how to handle objections, become an expert at executing winning sales negotiations, and learn the techniques to master the complex sale.', '2012-01-31', '2012-03-29 15:21:56', 'Buying the process, sales, sales calls, overcoming objectives, sales negotiations', 'Discover how the buying process actually works and how to handle objections, become an expert at winning sales negotiations, and learn the techniques to master the sa'),
(12, 'Generating Sales Leads', '\r\n<p>You canâ€™t close sales if you donâ€™t have leads, so maximizing the lead generation processes in your company is critical for business growth. In this course, youâ€™ll learn how to present yourself in a way that generates interest in what you do--a skill that is critical for power networking, which we will also explore.</p>\r\n<p>Weâ€™ll also delve into how to generate more referrals, which are some of the best leads you can find, and offer lots of tips on other ways you might not have thought of for uncovering more leads.Â  Weâ€™ll also talk about how to evaluate which of the lead generation engines youâ€™re using is working best.</p>\r\n', '2012-01-31', '2012-03-15 13:06:52', '', ''),
(13, 'Managing Your Finances', 'Managing your finances is more than having someone in your office pay the bills (maybe itâ€™s even you!). Savvy business owners understand financial reporting basics and, just as importantly, they can interpret what the reports are telling them. If you need help in this area, or just want a refresher, this course digs into those basics so that you are always prepared to make informed decisions.', '2012-01-31', '2012-03-29 15:19:17', 'finance, small business finances, finances, managing finances ', 'This course digs into those basics of managing your finances so that you are always prepared to make informed decisions.'),
(14, 'Running Your Business Smoothly', 'Itâ€™s an old adage, but you know it to be true: as a small business owner, you wear many hats.  Thereâ€™s a lot to keep track of, sales to be making, product issues to deal with, bills to payâ€”how do you manage it all and still keep your business running smoothly. In this course, weâ€™ve brought in a Human Resources professional and several productivity experts to give you the tools you need to keep you on top of things.', '2012-01-31', '2012-03-29 15:20:04', 'project planning, hr, human resources, small business hr tips  ', 'Weâ€™ve brought in a Human Resources professional and several productivity experts to give you the tools you need to keep your small business running smoothly.');
