(9, 'The Pain-Free Business Plan for Those Who Seek Long-Term Success', 'The Pain-Free Business Plan for Those Who Seek Long-Term Success', '2012-08-09 11:00:00', '2032-01-01 00:00:00', 'CST', 1, '&lt;p&gt;Having a business plan is paramount to your long-term growth. A good business plan conveys the excitement and promise of your business to any potential backer or future stakeholder. In this webinar, learn how to craft a professional plan that will wow any audience&amp;mdash;easy!&amp;nbsp; Master the ability to create, amend, or rework your small business plan&amp;mdash;without the headache.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;em&gt;Below are eight ways a business plan can ignite an explosion of growth within your business, by helping you:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;To sell &lt;em&gt;yourself&lt;/em&gt; on the business&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;To obtain bank financing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;To obtain investment funds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;To arrange strategic alliances&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;To obtain large contracts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;To attract key employees&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;To complete mergers and acquisitions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;To motivate and focus your management team&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Through visualization and reflection, we&amp;rsquo;ll help you discover ways to ensure your venture&amp;rsquo;s long-term success. &amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt; In this Business Accelerator Webinar you&amp;rsquo;ll also learn:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;A fresh new blueprint to approach the continuous growth of your businesses&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Why having a well-tailored business plan will lead you to where you want to go&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;How to construct a business plan you&amp;rsquo;ll actually use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Be prepared to get energized, think bigger, and have a solid start to your small business plan&amp;mdash;one that you can successfully build on&amp;mdash;minus the pain.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;This session will be led by Michael P. Valentine who is the CEO of OPEN PROS and author of the book &lt;em&gt;The ePill, Prescribed Empowerment for Today&amp;rsquo;s Entrepreneurs&lt;/em&gt;.&amp;nbsp; Known as &amp;ldquo;The Plan Doctor&amp;rdquo; to his clients, Valentine has aided hundreds of clients worldwide grow healthy and sustainable ventures.&lt;/p&gt;', 'hello, this is the description for this lovely event', '//c9890511.ssl.cf2.rackcdn.com/71333335246.jpg', 'Michael Valentine', 3, 1, 1, '', '', '', '', '2012-03-08 16:44:54', '2012-04-03 12:16:57'),
