(6, 'About the Business Accelerator Program', '<h3>It''s about taking your business to the next level</h3>\r\n<p>As a provider in commercial insurance products, American Family Insurance cares about helping small business owners survive and thrive during this challenging economic time. That''s why we have partnered with nationally recognized business coaches to offer this <strong>FREE</strong> program to give you valuable tools and strategies to build your business.</p>\r\n<h3>Online, in person, or both...it''s your choice</h3>\r\n<p>The Business Accelerator Program is uniquely designed to deliver business coaching in a community environment that will challenge the way you operate today and encourage sharing of ideas among participants. Participants can join the program at any time--all sessions are recorded and available on demand to match your schedule. You''ll learn through:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Bootcamps</li>\r\n  <li>Webinars</li>\r\n  <li>Online coaching forum</li>\r\n  <li>Eâ€“tips</li>\r\n  <li>Tips &amp; Tools</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>FREE education that every small business needs</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><strong>Marketing</strong>â€”understand your sweet spot and communicate it well; learn how to leverage affordable marketing tools for ultimate impact</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Sales</strong>â€”build your sales system and your skills, and learn how to leverage Facebook and LinkedIn to increase your number of sales calls</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Finance &amp; Growth</strong>â€”learn how to plan for your business based on your profit &amp; loss statement and understand your financing options</li>\r\n  <li><strong>More</strong>â€”find out the secrets to hiring Aâ€“players and managing tough personnel issues as well as how to manage risk in your business</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 1, 'Through webinars, boot camps, online coaching forms and e-tips we offer free educational opportunities to help small business in marketing, sales, along with finance and growth and more! ', 'small business, education, marketing, sales, tips, business tips', '', 9, '2012-03-19 16:36:34', '2012-06-02 12:59:27'),
(7, 'FAQ', '&lt;div class=&quot;question&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;accordionFAQ&quot;&gt;What will I have to pay to be in the Business Accelerator Program?&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;accordionC&quot;&gt;Nothing, it&#039;s free! American Family Insurance is underwriting all expenses associated with this program.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;question&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;accordionFAQ&quot;&gt;If I did not attend the Symposium in May, can I still participate in the Business Accelerator Program?&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;accordionC&quot;&gt;Yes, all symposiums and webinars are available online, on-demand, so you can join the program at any time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;question&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;accordionFAQ&quot;&gt;Where can I find the recordings of the Symposium and the teleconferences from last year?&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;accordionC&quot;&gt;Only program members can access these recordings. Once you&#039;ve enrolled in the program and have signed in, simply go to the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.amfambusinessaccelerator.com/go-to-class/index.php&quot;&gt;Go to Class&lt;/a&gt; page. From there you can select Webinar or Symposium to see all that is available in our archive.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;question&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;accordionFAQ&quot;&gt;Who is able to participate in the Business Accelerator?&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;accordionC&quot;&gt;All business owners are welcome to participate in the program. Business Accelerator is intended for owners and partners, however, rather than their staff.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;question&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;accordionFAQ&quot;&gt;Why must I register and sign-in to access the Business Accelerator materials or talk with the coaches?&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;accordionC&quot;&gt;The information provided to you via the Business Accelerator program is highly valued in the marketplace. That&#039;s why we&#039;ve created a secured area to hold the Business Accelerator curriculum and the Coaching Forum. Since the program is free, we just ask that all participants register so that we may know who is obtaining this information. In addition, we want all of our Business Accelerator members to feel comfortable that their interactions with the coaches will be kept within the Business Accelerator community.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;', '', 1, '', '', '', 9, '2012-03-20 14:38:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(8, 'Protect My Business  ', '<p>Let American Family Insurance equip you with everything you need to develop your business and keep it covered.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class="gotham blue">Outstanding Protection </h3>\r\n<p>No matter the size of your business, American Family offers products and services to keep you covered.\r\n<a href="http://www.amfam.com/products/business/default.asp">Discover Our Products</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class="gotham blue">Local Agent</h3>\r\n<p>Our agents - small business owners themselves - live in your community and are ready to help you find the best coverage for your business needs.\r\n<a href="http://apps.amfam.com/agentlocator">Find an Agent Near You</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class="gotham blue">Landlord Toolbox</h3>\r\n<p>If you own or manage rental property, we have resources to help you before you hand over the keys. <a href="http://www.amfam.com/microsites/landlordtoolbox/">Open Our Toolbox</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class="gotham blue">Safety Advisor</h3>\r\n<p>Our quarterly e-newsletter is filled with tips for protecting your workforce - and your bottom line.\r\n<a href="https://pc.mypreferences.com/amfam/SignUp.aspx">Sign up Today</a></p>', '', 1, '', '', '', 9, '2012-03-20 21:01:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
